name: EARLY STARKID 02
description:
STARKIDs are a species of highly intelligent cosmic entities from the GOMAVERSE.

SUBJECT 02 seems to be in an emotional state of cosmic confusion. Be very cautious when making contact with a STARKID. Especially when the individual is in a seemingly disruptive attitude. 

This creature is capable of destroying entire cities with ease. 

DANGER LEVEL: [DEMON]

ADDITIONAL INFORMATION: [STARKIDs are able to communicate telepathically. Interestingly enough STARKIDs can form BONDS with particular individuals of the GOMAVERSE, despite their violent and unpredictable behavior]
 
ART by GOMA
